name: Go, Diego Go! Great Dinosaur Rescue
name_original: Go, Diego Go! Great Dinosaur Rescue
description:
Go, Diego Go! Great Dinosaur Rescue is a puzzle-platformer game developed by High Voltage Software and Black Lantern Studios. It was originally released in 2008. 2K Play published the game. The game is rated as "Meh" on RAWG.
You can play Go, Diego Go! Great Dinosaur Rescue on Wii, Nintendo DS, PC and PlayStation 2.
